  "detailed_description": "<strong>Nightmares Mansion: Scary Dreams</strong> is a first-person adventure horror game with puzzle elements, a tense and exciting atmosphere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879770/extras/422ebc2191e8ddafa59da949f47dbb84.poster.avif?t=1730217481\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879770/extras/422ebc2191e8ddafa59da949f47dbb84.webm?t=1730217481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879770/extras/422ebc2191e8ddafa59da949f47dbb84.mp4?t=1730217481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SYNOPSIS</h2><br>You slept and have woken up, embraced by profound and suffocating shadows. The surrounding area is dark and oppressive. Someone has captured you in your dream and turned it into horror. But who? How can you escape from here? And most importantly, does the girl in the red stand as an ally or enemy in this horror tableau?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879770/extras/f57a2105ff44c02445a5d2bca79c8efd.poster.avif?t=1730217481\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879770/extras/f57a2105ff44c02445a5d2bca79c8efd.webm?t=1730217481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879770/extras/f57a2105ff44c02445a5d2bca79c8efd.mp4?t=1730217481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEHOLD, THE KEY FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>This house is a labyrinthine repository of kidnapped souls. Interact with them and engage with this scary mansion to uncover the mystery. <br></li><li>This world is not like the real one. What manner of place is this, and whence lies its threshold? You have to solve all the puzzles in the game and discover the secrets of its master, and perhaps, salvation shall be yours.<br></li><li>Explore subjects: terrifying things, mysterious notes, traces of dark forces everywhere. <br></li><li>Walk around the house, open doors, solve puzzles, use hints, heed the omens, and the narrative will unfold before you.<br></li><li>A tense ambiance with suspense, mystery, and the sudden horror screamers await you.<br></li><li>Collect the grimoires to pierce the veil, uncover the truth, discover the secret, and escape the mansion.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INCLUDED WITHIN</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three chapters, a triad of demonic sentinels, and a trinity of the horror house. <br></li><li>A stunning horror environment expands as you dare to tread its forsaken halls.<br></li><li>Tread carefully, for you are both the protagonist and the prize in this narrative.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879770/extras/649484e6cc602643f70b1f1c0e84c287.poster.avif?t=1730217481\" width=500 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879770/extras/649484e6cc602643f70b1f1c0e84c287.webm?t=1730217481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879770/extras/649484e6cc602643f70b1f1c0e84c287.mp4?t=1730217481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
